Q_DESC:
To write a program in which the user has to perform operations in a linked list.
 To input a Linked List which has data members sorted in ascending order. Task is to construct a Balanced Binary Search Tree which has same data members as the given Linked List and display the pre order traversal of the BST.
INPUT:
9 7 6 5 4 3 2// linked list 
OUTPUT:
Given Linked List 2 3 4 5 6 7 9 
PreOrder Traversal of constructed BST 5 3 2 4 7 6 9
TESTCASE_1:
7 6 5 4 3 2 1

Given Linked List 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 
PreOrder Traversal of constructed BST 4 2 1 3 6 5 7
